        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/Ancestral/scene_bulldog.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 45ce89bb-0689-4b63-9f5e-5db1723904bf).Image",
        "Description": "Greetings, agent Necros.\rYour mission is to infiltrate an MI6 safehouse operating at Thornbridge Manor. There you will extract our comrade, General Georgi Koskov, from British custody. You will use explosives to create the look of an out-of-control gas leak. Kills are permitted in service of this goal. General Koskov will conceal himself in a hearse parked on site during the chaos. You must simply obtain the nearby key and make your escape under the noses of MI6.\rGood luck, comrade!",
